WEBVTT

00:00:00.602 --> 00:00:04.024
-LEK HAREVII SHEL HARAYON IM GEVERET

00:00:04.024 --> 00:00:05.692
FANIAH ZELBST

00:00:05.749 --> 00:00:06.873
BEVAKASHA.

00:00:09.664 --> 00:00:11.649
di mishpokhe SZYDLOWSKI

00:00:12.010 --> 00:00:15.716
di oreme mishpokhe, di ⟨ibergebende⟩ mishpokhe far undz

00:00:16.212 --> 00:00:18.132
vos hot gezukht undzer

00:00:18.132 --> 00:00:19.496
gutskeyt

00:00:20.008 --> 00:00:21.639
hobn ayngeshpant zeyer

00:00:21.814 --> 00:00:24.744
klyatshe, avekgeforn in Disne

00:00:24.835 --> 00:00:26.316
tsu der galekhte

00:00:26.316 --> 00:00:28.119
un dertseylt di geshikhte

00:00:28.395 --> 00:00:29.126
az zi hot

00:00:29.126 --> 00:00:32.468
Khaye Fuks darf hobn a kind, tsi zey kenen

00:00:32.468 --> 00:00:33.857
kumen tsu ir.

00:00:34.167 --> 00:00:36.355
zi hot barat zikh mit ir man

00:00:36.900 --> 00:00:39.071
nu, zey hobn bashtimt az me meg kumen.

00:00:40.123 --> 00:00:42.617
in a vokh arum, oykh zuntik

00:00:42.617 --> 00:00:43.790
nor zuntik

00:00:43.790 --> 00:00:46.360
vayl az me fort in mitn vokh falt a khshad

00:00:46.360 --> 00:00:49.110
nokh vos fort der SZYDLOWSKI in shtot arayn?

00:00:49.110 --> 00:00:52.267
iz nor zuntik oder fraytik tsu mark

00:00:54.096 --> 00:00:55.898
dos iz mistomen geven fraytik.

00:00:55.898 --> 00:00:58.388
mayn shvester mitn shvoger hobn gezogt

00:00:58.388 --> 00:01:00.553
"Fanye, kum oykh mit undz forn.

00:01:01.352 --> 00:01:04.299
di galekhte hot gezogt az mir veln do blaybn lebn.

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:07.753
kum oykh mit undz. vos vestu blaybn aleyn?"

00:01:07.753 --> 00:01:09.075
zog ikh "neyn.

00:01:09.857 --> 00:01:13.296
ikh bin antlofn, vos vet zayn mit mir veys ikh nit

00:01:13.296 --> 00:01:15.032
nor ikh vel shoyn n-

00:01:15.139 --> 00:01:17.090
blaybn do in di derfer."

00:01:17.670 --> 00:01:19.891
zey zaynen avekgeforn in shtot.

00:01:20.455 --> 00:01:22.237
oyf a tsveytn tog

00:01:22.294 --> 00:01:23.992
hot ver gemasert

00:01:24.336 --> 00:01:26.241
az mayn shvester Khaye

00:01:26.241 --> 00:01:27.751
iz bay der galekhte.

00:01:27.751 --> 00:01:29.431
in mitn heln tog

00:01:29.431 --> 00:01:32.291
hot men ir gefirt, un m'hot ir geshosn

00:01:32.291 --> 00:01:33.701
oyf dem zelbn ort

00:01:33.701 --> 00:01:37.311
lebn di tsvey groyse kvorim iz dort-o mayn shvester

00:01:37.380 --> 00:01:38.251
oykh

00:01:38.595 --> 00:01:39.984
dershosn gevorn.

00:01:39.984 --> 00:01:42.394
afile genoye date veys ikh nit ven

00:01:42.394 --> 00:01:44.444
nor in a, oyf morgn

00:01:44.444 --> 00:01:46.454
⟨vi⟩ iz gekumen

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:48.101
tsu der galekhte

00:01:48.101 --> 00:01:50.334
der shvoger iz geblibn aleyn.

00:01:51.505 --> 00:01:52.413
dan

00:01:52.413 --> 00:01:55.076
hobn di daytshn aroysgegebn a bafel

00:01:55.622 --> 00:02:00.307
un zaynen geforn di daytshn in di derfer, arum di velder.

00:02:00.786 --> 00:02:02.074
"yidn

00:02:02.074 --> 00:02:05.235
ir zayt in di velder. geyt aroys fun di velder.

00:02:05.410 --> 00:02:07.648
di daytshn lozn aykh lebn.

00:02:07.889 --> 00:02:09.975
ir zayt nutslekhe JUDEN

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:11.951
un mir lozn aykh lebn."

00:02:12.582 --> 00:02:13.639
iz dan

00:02:13.982 --> 00:02:16.608
iz geven gleyb ikh a fuftsn yidn

00:02:16.767 --> 00:02:19.478
iz dan mayn shvoger Khaim Fridman

00:02:20.361 --> 00:02:21.620
oykh arayn

00:02:22.572 --> 00:02:24.928
in di grupe nutslekhe yidn.

00:02:25.643 --> 00:02:27.949
m'hot zey gegebn a dire

00:02:28.056 --> 00:02:32.707
zey hobn gearbet, shtil ruik, vi keyn mol gornisht nit.

00:02:35.633 --> 00:02:37.112
er hot gevust

00:02:37.219 --> 00:02:39.288
az ikh bin in dorf

00:02:39.447 --> 00:02:41.038
in ⟨a⟩ vinter

00:02:41.038 --> 00:02:42.917
on shikh, a borvese

00:02:42.973 --> 00:02:45.566
hot er gegebn a shuster

00:02:45.758 --> 00:02:48.030
zoln mir oyfneyen shtivelekh.

00:02:49.268 --> 00:02:50.443
oyf vinter.

00:02:52.204 --> 00:02:53.295
ober

00:02:53.352 --> 00:02:56.113
di shtivl vos zaynen geblibn ⟨bay dem⟩ poyer

00:02:56.119 --> 00:03:01.901
vayl in dray monatn arum hot men di nutslekhe yidn alemen oysgeshosn.

00:03:02.937 --> 00:03:04.821
⟨un zey hot⟩ tsugezogt tsu lebn

00:03:05.097 --> 00:03:07.296
un m'hot zey gemakht an aktsye

00:03:07.296 --> 00:03:12.178
dos iz geven di letste yidn vos m'hot oysgeshosn fun Disner geto.

00:03:12.471 --> 00:03:16.295
der, der galekh, di galekhte iz gevezn AUCH VOS Disne?

00:03:16.391 --> 00:03:20.210
in Disne, ober zi iz a goye, vos is a KOMER's a froy

00:03:18.377 --> 00:03:19.265
yo

00:03:19.795 --> 00:03:21.696
JA, dos iz gevezn fun Disne?

00:03:23.102 --> 00:03:23.838
ye.

00:03:24.604 --> 00:03:26.505
yetst heybt zikh far mir on

00:03:27.473 --> 00:03:28.980
a naye TKUFA.

00:03:28.980 --> 00:03:30.622
ikh bin geblibn aleyn.

00:03:31.455 --> 00:03:32.647
ikh zits

00:03:33.784 --> 00:03:35.077
oyf di shtroy

00:03:35.404 --> 00:03:37.423
bay SZYDLOWSKIn in shtal

00:03:38.121 --> 00:03:39.448
un ikh her

00:03:39.792 --> 00:03:42.531
vi di vorones, dos zenen azoyne feygelekh

00:03:42.531 --> 00:03:44.426
shvartse zaynen zey azoyne

00:03:45.192 --> 00:03:47.565
oyf, bay undz heysn zey vorones.

00:03:49.545 --> 00:03:52.661
ikh her az zey klapn in dakh, in dakh.

00:03:53.022 --> 00:03:54.130
in GAG.

00:03:54.473 --> 00:03:55.549
klapn

00:03:55.549 --> 00:03:58.905
mit di UNK klapn, klapn, klapn, hunderter vorones.

00:03:59.822 --> 00:04:02.010
trakht ikh epes hot pasirt.

00:04:02.353 --> 00:04:04.034
epes iz nit gut

00:04:04.159 --> 00:04:07.241
az di vorones klapn mir in dakh in kop arayn.

00:04:09.340 --> 00:04:11.781
zaynen gekumen tsu mir SZYDLOWSKIS

00:04:12.428 --> 00:04:16.522
zog ikh "vos batayt azoy vi di vorones hobn mir geklapt a gantse tog?"

00:04:18.148 --> 00:04:21.416
nu, zogn zey "Fanye, mir muzn dir dertseyln dem emes.

00:04:22.519 --> 00:04:24.228
mit tsvey vokhn tsurik

00:04:24.228 --> 00:04:26.394
hot men geshosn dayn shvester.

00:04:29.185 --> 00:04:31.392
zey hobn gevust az m'hot ir geshosn

00:04:31.392 --> 00:04:33.617
nor mir hobn zey nit dertseylt.

00:04:34.028 --> 00:04:35.794
ober ikh hob glaykh farshtanen

00:04:36.255 --> 00:04:37.863
az di krakeray fun f-

00:04:37.863 --> 00:04:41.042
fun di feygl hobn mir keyn guts nit ongezogt.

00:04:42.432 --> 00:04:44.096
bin ikh geblibn aleyn.

00:04:44.592 --> 00:04:46.459
zey hobn mir zeyer baruikt.

00:04:47.022 --> 00:04:48.703
me zogt "Fanye

00:04:48.912 --> 00:04:50.830
du bist undzer tokhter.

00:04:51.240 --> 00:04:53.782
mir veln far dir zayn vi eltern

00:04:54.177 --> 00:04:56.977
nor du zetst dikh aleyn bay undz in shtub

00:04:56.977 --> 00:04:58.777
ken men nit zayn keyn sakh tsayt.

00:04:59.003 --> 00:05:00.617
mir zaynen shnayder.

00:05:01.332 --> 00:05:03.941
tsu undz kumen a sakh klyentn

00:05:04.622 --> 00:05:07.501
neyen un tsunemen arbet un mestn

00:05:08.757 --> 00:05:10.590
un undz in shtub zetst dikh.

00:05:10.714 --> 00:05:12.584
iz geven eyn tsimer

00:05:12.584 --> 00:05:14.550
un a shloftsimer iz geven

00:05:14.550 --> 00:05:17.191
a, a shafe iz geven opgeteylt

00:05:17.191 --> 00:05:18.971
fun zeyer shloftsimer

00:05:18.971 --> 00:05:21.440
mitn salon vu er hot geneyt.

00:05:22.020 --> 00:05:26.097
un di kinder zaynen geshlofn oyf azoyne lange

00:05:27.792 --> 00:05:29.468
SAPOT azoyne

00:05:27.910 --> 00:05:29.051
vayter

00:05:29.468 --> 00:05:34.839
un eyn-, a meydele, MARUSHYA, iz geshlofn oyfn oyvn, oyfn rusishn oyvn

00:05:35.419 --> 00:05:38.281
un tsvey kinder mistome oyf der erd geshlofn.

00:05:38.895 --> 00:05:42.348
ober zaynen geven gezunte, yunge, oreme.

00:05:43.198 --> 00:05:44.508
zeyer muter

00:05:44.903 --> 00:05:47.546
hot geshpilt gedenk ikh oyf a balalayke

00:05:48.261 --> 00:05:51.646
un az zi volt visn es kumen tsu zey mentshn

00:05:51.646 --> 00:05:54.596
volt zi mir take shpiln oyf der balalayke

00:05:54.596 --> 00:05:56.737
az ikh zol visn, far mir

00:05:56.737 --> 00:05:57.756
a simen

00:05:57.795 --> 00:06:00.776
az ikh zol visn vi f- tsu, nit rirn zikh.

00:06:00.782 --> 00:06:04.134
vayl oyb ikh bin gelegn hintern shafe bahaltn

00:06:04.697 --> 00:06:07.276
zol ikh visn az ikh zol zayn vi a geshtorbene

00:06:07.276 --> 00:06:08.896
nit rirn zikh fun ort.

00:06:11.464 --> 00:06:12.707
bay nakht

00:06:15.278 --> 00:06:16.993
eyn un draysikste

00:06:17.674 --> 00:06:18.883
detsember

00:06:17.674 --> 00:06:18.900
detsember

00:06:19.530 --> 00:06:21.380
tsvey un fertsikstn yor

00:06:22.585 --> 00:06:24.148
zaynen umgekumen

00:06:24.441 --> 00:06:27.759
tsvey bokherim oykh fun mayn shtot Disne.

00:06:28.120 --> 00:06:30.746
Sushkevitsh iz zeyer familye.

00:06:31.393 --> 00:06:33.850
zey zaynen geven fun baruf

00:06:34.296 --> 00:06:37.125
fun felkhlekh voltn zey makhn

00:06:38.025 --> 00:06:39.048
leder.

00:06:39.358 --> 00:06:40.207
dos heyst

00:06:40.207 --> 00:06:42.120
az me shekht di shepsn

00:06:42.632 --> 00:06:43.740
iz di

00:06:44.843 --> 00:06:46.524
di shepsene fel

00:06:46.598 --> 00:06:48.752
leygt men in azoyne

00:06:50.040 --> 00:06:51.370
betshkes

00:06:51.370 --> 00:06:52.329
KADIM.

00:06:52.723 --> 00:06:54.303
dortn leygt men

00:06:54.698 --> 00:06:57.276
kh- materyel un azoyne vapne

00:06:57.276 --> 00:06:59.242
un s- dos iz geven zeyer baruf.

00:06:59.242 --> 00:07:03.889
in a vokh arum in tsvey reynikt men dos, un dos bakumt zikh reyne

00:07:04.536 --> 00:07:06.119
reyne f- fel

00:07:06.119 --> 00:07:08.161
vos me neyt shikh, shtivl

00:07:08.161 --> 00:07:09.795
dos iz geven zeyer arbet.

00:07:10.712 --> 00:07:11.797
iz ot di

00:07:11.797 --> 00:07:13.097
tsvey brider

00:07:13.097 --> 00:07:15.195
un zeyer a kuzin, ⟨der⟩ Lekekh

00:07:15.825 --> 00:07:17.641
hobn gearbet bay dem

00:07:17.648 --> 00:07:20.089
un zey zaynen geven oysgebahaltn

00:07:20.668 --> 00:07:22.248
bay a poyer

00:07:23.082 --> 00:07:26.366
mistome tsvey hundert meter fun mayn SZYDLOWSKIn.

00:07:28.482 --> 00:07:30.248
zuntik in der fri

00:07:31.587 --> 00:07:35.530
vil mayn poyer mit der mishpokhe forn

00:07:35.890 --> 00:07:37.487
in TSERKEV

00:07:38.708 --> 00:07:40.035
⟨modlen⟩ zikh

00:07:40.075 --> 00:07:41.537
vi bay di goyim

00:07:41.712 --> 00:07:43.984
geyt men a zuntik in kloyster

00:07:44.479 --> 00:07:45.789
⟨modlen⟩ zikh.

00:07:46.133 --> 00:07:48.669
dervayle viln zey hern a bisl nayes.

00:07:48.669 --> 00:07:53.181
er veyst dokh az bay im zitst dokh oyfn oyvn a yidishke

00:07:53.389 --> 00:07:55.453
iz zi ⟨zogt⟩ "hert ir dokh mit

00:07:55.453 --> 00:07:57.517
UNK vos tut zikh."

00:07:57.912 --> 00:07:59.857
ersht er geyt aroys fun shtub.

00:07:59.857 --> 00:08:00.996
er zet

00:08:00.996 --> 00:08:03.339
mentshn shteyn fun vaytn

00:08:03.362 --> 00:08:06.412
tsvey tsuzamen, dray tsuzamen, fir tsuzamen.

00:08:06.412 --> 00:08:09.082
me redt, me makht ⟨epes⟩ mit di hent, me redt.

00:08:09.454 --> 00:08:14.223
iz er tsu zitsung gegangen, zogt er "vo- vos iz do? vos kumt ir for? ir kumt dokh nit in kloyster?"

00:08:14.685 --> 00:08:18.408
zogn zey "du veyst nit vos iz geven hayntik ⟨in ovnt⟩?" zogt er "ikh veys nit."

00:08:19.343 --> 00:08:20.673
zogt er "Ru-

00:08:20.673 --> 00:08:23.674
Ruvtshinke's yinglekh hot men dort geshosn."

00:08:24.608 --> 00:08:27.116
"vi azoy?" ot hobn zey dertseylt.

00:08:27.595 --> 00:08:31.065
kol zman di yinglekh hobn gearbet

00:08:31.071 --> 00:08:33.292
un nokh epes tsugetsolt

00:08:34.833 --> 00:08:36.613
iz geven alts in ordenung.

00:08:36.613 --> 00:08:40.823
UNK vi zey hobn nit gehat mit vos tsu tsoln, un keyn arbet iz shoyn mer nit geven

00:08:40.943 --> 00:08:42.810
darf men dokh umbrengen zey.

00:08:42.917 --> 00:08:46.719
zaynen zey avekgeforn in der dorf NIKOLAYEVO

00:08:46.719 --> 00:08:48.716
un gebrakht tsvey daytshn

00:08:50.055 --> 00:08:51.601
un der balebos

00:08:51.642 --> 00:08:53.866
hot gemakht a rusishe bod

00:08:53.866 --> 00:08:56.067
vayl bay undz in Vaysrusland

00:08:56.067 --> 00:09:00.427
i- i- yeder poyer hot a UNK aza, a bod.

00:09:00.670 --> 00:09:02.318
dos iz oyf shteyner.

00:09:03.218 --> 00:09:06.941
es brenen zikh on shteyner. me gist arop vaser

00:09:07.251 --> 00:09:09.658
oyf di shteyner, un s'vert a pare

00:09:10.035 --> 00:09:13.303
un dos iz geven undzere beder in dorf.

00:09:15.199 --> 00:09:16.374
der poyer

00:09:16.431 --> 00:09:21.431
hot ayngehitst aza bod far di dray yidishe yinglekh, der kleyner gornisht.

00:09:21.431 --> 00:09:24.187
zey hobn zikh oysgeton, un zey vashn zikh.

00:09:25.442 --> 00:09:26.730
un di vaser

00:09:26.730 --> 00:09:29.216
iz geven derbay a sazhlke.

00:09:29.560 --> 00:09:31.022
a BRICHA aza.

00:09:31.602 --> 00:09:33.387
geyen aroys di bokherim

00:09:33.387 --> 00:09:35.173
nemen di kalte vaser

00:09:35.550 --> 00:09:39.150
un gisn aroyf oyf di shteyner, un vayter iz varem in bod.

00:09:39.150 --> 00:09:40.095
un azoy

00:09:40.095 --> 00:09:44.150
dortn azoy ongenumen. shoyn gants gezunt, der SAUNA zet es oys.

00:09:45.743 --> 00:09:46.766
PITOM

00:09:47.127 --> 00:09:48.639
di tsvey daytshn

00:09:49.354 --> 00:09:52.672
hobn arumgerungen, arumgeringlt di bod

00:09:53.185 --> 00:09:55.474
un geshrien "HIER AUS, HIER AUS."

00:09:55.952 --> 00:09:57.493
zey veysn gornit.

00:09:57.493 --> 00:10:01.203
zaynen zey aroysgelofn fun bod, dray nakete bokherim

00:10:01.203 --> 00:10:04.003
eyn un draysik detsember, ven s'iz geven

00:10:04.003 --> 00:10:06.814
minus finf un tsvantsik grad frost

00:10:07.798 --> 00:10:08.855
minimum

00:10:10.397 --> 00:10:12.281
un di daytshn hobn glaykh

00:10:13.401 --> 00:10:14.947
geshosn oyf an ort.

00:10:15.139 --> 00:10:15.963
tsvey

00:10:15.963 --> 00:10:18.761
tsvey daytshn hobn tsvey yidn geshosn.

00:10:18.835 --> 00:10:21.613
un der driter bokherl, Lekekh

00:10:22.193 --> 00:10:25.058
hot bavizn in dem moment tsu antloyfn.

00:10:25.058 --> 00:10:26.304
a naketer

00:10:26.530 --> 00:10:29.342
oyfn frost, oyfn shney, un gelofn.

00:10:29.483 --> 00:10:31.637
veys men dokh nit vu er iz gelofn.

00:10:32.689 --> 00:10:33.965
dertseyln

00:10:34.123 --> 00:10:35.433
di poyerim

00:10:35.794 --> 00:10:37.323
mayn SZYDLOWSKIn

00:10:37.802 --> 00:10:40.465
az dos hot geshen hayntike nakht

00:10:40.465 --> 00:10:41.925
tsvey bokherim

00:10:41.925 --> 00:10:44.015
Ruvtshinke's hot men geshosn

00:10:44.015 --> 00:10:45.905
un der driter iz antlofn

00:10:45.905 --> 00:10:49.795
un m'hot, un di daytshn hobn gezukht, fun shtub tsu shtub gezukht

00:10:49.851 --> 00:10:51.380
un im not gefunen.

00:10:52.804 --> 00:10:55.450
mayn poyer iz sh- shoyn arayn in noz

00:10:55.450 --> 00:10:57.844
az UNK hot a sakone mit mir

00:10:58.677 --> 00:11:01.539
vayl mayn shtub hot nokh nit, nit gezukht

00:11:03.300 --> 00:11:07.091
tsu mir hobn dokh, tsu im heyst es, nit gekumen zukhn bay nakht.

00:11:07.384 --> 00:11:09.439
far vos take iz men nit gekumen?

00:11:09.439 --> 00:11:11.229
vayl di daytshn zaynen gegangen

00:11:11.229 --> 00:11:14.779
vu s'iz groyse hayzer, vu s'iz likht in di hayzer

00:11:14.779 --> 00:11:16.549
un do iz dokh geven an oreme

00:11:16.549 --> 00:11:18.109
shitbl aza, un a

00:11:18.109 --> 00:11:20.939
a niderike, mit a shtroyenem dakh

00:11:20.939 --> 00:11:22.515
iz vos veln geyn daytshn

00:11:22.740 --> 00:11:24.995
zukhn in aza oreme hayzke?

00:11:27.313 --> 00:11:28.812
hobn zey durkhgelozn

00:11:28.812 --> 00:11:30.125
mayn SZYDLOWSKIn.

00:11:30.992 --> 00:11:32.049
iz arayn

00:11:32.967 --> 00:11:34.837
der SZYDLOWSKI DIMITRI

00:11:34.837 --> 00:11:36.437
tsu mir in shtub

00:11:36.696 --> 00:11:39.081
un gezogt tsu di gantse mishpokhe

00:11:39.081 --> 00:11:41.533
"kinderlekh, kumt ale in droysn.

00:11:41.573 --> 00:11:44.368
ale, mir forn hayntik in kloyster

00:11:45.032 --> 00:11:47.388
vayle mir hobn gekent di bokherim

00:11:48.711 --> 00:11:51.665
vayl zey hobn gearbet umetum, bay yeder poyer iz geven

00:11:51.665 --> 00:11:53.545
shepsn, geven felkhlekh

00:11:53.545 --> 00:11:56.332
un ⟨zey hobn⟩ zikh farnumen, ikh gleyb a yor tsayt mit dem.

00:11:57.182 --> 00:11:58.441
kinderlekh

00:11:58.650 --> 00:12:02.508
"ir zolt keynem nit dertseyln vos hot pasirt, nor geyt nit arayn in shtub.

00:12:03.021 --> 00:12:04.871
zayt mit undz in droysn."

00:12:05.839 --> 00:12:07.757
un di froy SZYDLOWSKA

00:12:08.522 --> 00:12:11.891
mit dem man zaynen arayn tsu mir in shtub.

00:12:12.589 --> 00:12:15.316
zey hobn mir gegebn a fleshele neft

00:12:16.892 --> 00:12:20.998
un mir dertseylt az di brider hot men tsvey geshosn

00:12:20.998 --> 00:12:22.269
un der driter

00:12:22.343 --> 00:12:23.995
hot men nit gefunen

00:12:23.995 --> 00:12:26.985
"iz meglekh az hayntike nakht veln zey kumen d-

00:12:26.985 --> 00:12:29.695
aher zukhn, un du bist do

00:12:29.700 --> 00:12:31.415
un mir kenen ⟨dir⟩ nit

00:12:31.725 --> 00:12:34.523
heysn geyn in mitn heln tog fun shtub

00:12:34.523 --> 00:12:36.664
vayl ale shteyen dokh in droysn.

00:12:36.838 --> 00:12:41.017
PITOM vet men derzen az di yidishke geyt arayn fun undzer shtub

00:12:41.108 --> 00:12:43.340
zaynen mir dokh in a sakone.

00:12:43.340 --> 00:12:45.421
iz gedenk, FANYA DAVIDOVNA

00:12:46.052 --> 00:12:47.666
ot iz di fleshl

00:12:47.689 --> 00:12:48.732
neft

00:12:48.732 --> 00:12:50.652
un ot zaynen di shvebelekh.

00:12:51.368 --> 00:12:52.824
un az du vest hern

00:12:52.824 --> 00:12:56.064
az di daytshn dernentern zikh tsu undzer shtub

00:12:56.064 --> 00:12:58.635
vayl zey shrayen do, zey geyen nit shtil.

00:12:58.962 --> 00:13:02.384
vi du vest nor derhern zeyere geshreyen fun di DEUTSCHEN

00:13:02.384 --> 00:13:04.642
zolstu glaykh untertsindn

00:13:04.851 --> 00:13:07.410
di shtub, bagisn di tir

00:13:07.517 --> 00:13:08.945
mit di neft

00:13:09.964 --> 00:13:11.730
un azoy oyf di vent

00:13:11.871 --> 00:13:13.738
un zolst untertsindn

00:13:14.419 --> 00:13:16.488
oyb du vest kenen, zolstu antloyfn

00:13:16.528 --> 00:13:19.205
un oyb nit iz, ot dos iz dayn goyrl."

00:13:20.697 --> 00:13:24.229
ober mayn goyrl iz geven az di daytshn zaynen nit gekumen.

00:13:24.229 --> 00:13:26.124
un di shtub iz geblibn

00:13:26.248 --> 00:13:28.689
nor di shrek iz geblibn far alemen.

00:13:29.893 --> 00:13:31.591
zey kumen farnakht.

00:13:31.834 --> 00:13:34.345
der tog iz durkhgegangen besholem, shtil.

00:13:34.345 --> 00:13:36.823
keyn daytshn ⟨zaynen⟩ mir nit gekumen zukhn

00:13:36.829 --> 00:13:39.286
yene, yenem bokherl Lekekh

00:13:39.563 --> 00:13:42.341
un zey hobn mir gezogt "FANYA DAVIDOVNA

00:13:42.448 --> 00:13:44.551
mir veln dir avekfirn

00:13:45.402 --> 00:13:47.952
nokh zeyer a gute froy.

00:13:47.952 --> 00:13:49.352
zi iz a, a, ka- a

00:13:49.352 --> 00:13:50.542
katoylishe.

00:13:50.542 --> 00:13:52.272
zi iz zeyer a gleybike

00:13:52.272 --> 00:13:53.422
a gute

00:13:53.422 --> 00:13:54.980
iz zi a shnayderke

00:13:55.493 --> 00:13:58.423
un mir veln ir dir avekfirn."

00:13:58.767 --> 00:14:00.870
zey hobn ayngeshpant di ferd

00:14:01.315 --> 00:14:04.042
avekgeleygt oyfn veg shtroy

00:14:04.420 --> 00:14:06.644
mit hey, mir

00:14:06.644 --> 00:14:09.054
ikh hob zikh avekgeleygt oyfn shlitn

00:14:10.731 --> 00:14:12.260
di shtroy mit di hey

00:14:12.418 --> 00:14:13.711
oyf mir

00:14:14.680 --> 00:14:17.846
un di kinderlekh zitsn oyf mir, un mir forn.

00:14:18.882 --> 00:14:20.935
vayl dos iz geven ershte

00:14:21.835 --> 00:14:23.442
eyn un draysik detsember.

00:14:23.442 --> 00:14:25.572
oyf morgn ershte yanuar.

00:14:25.572 --> 00:14:28.122
ershte yanuar iz dos, bay di

00:14:28.122 --> 00:14:31.822
katoylishe mit di PRAVOSLAVNI iz dos nay yor.

00:14:31.960 --> 00:14:34.029
geyt men vayter in kloyster

00:14:34.761 --> 00:14:37.674
iz kloymersht er fort in kloyster mit di kinder

00:14:38.440 --> 00:14:40.509
un mir hot men avekgefirt

00:14:41.697 --> 00:14:43.988
fartog ⟨flegt es⟩ geyn, fartog, fartog

00:14:43.988 --> 00:14:45.791
ven di zun iz nokh nit geven

00:14:46.118 --> 00:14:47.985
tsu a mishpokhe

00:14:48.430 --> 00:14:50.820
KODIS BOLESLAW.

00:14:53.323 --> 00:14:56.439
zey ⟨hobn⟩ geshtanen fun vayt un gekukt

00:14:56.547 --> 00:14:58.239
vos vet zayn mit mir

00:14:58.239 --> 00:14:59.797
un zaynen avekgeforn.

00:15:00.478 --> 00:15:05.298
ikh bin aropgegangen fun shlitn, aroysgegangen fun di hey mit di shtroy, in gantsn

00:15:05.507 --> 00:15:07.138
badekte mit dem

00:15:07.532 --> 00:15:10.918
⟨ober⟩ dos iz geven nokh di zun nit ⟨oyfgeyn⟩, MAMASH iz nokh geven fintster.

00:15:12.325 --> 00:15:15.204
un ikh gey. di hint hobn ongehoybn biln

00:15:17.522 --> 00:15:18.430
un

00:15:18.430 --> 00:15:20.031
un dortn iz geven

00:15:20.053 --> 00:15:23.965
aza RUCHEY o. dos heyst, di vaser geyt azoy sh-

00:15:23.965 --> 00:15:25.346
shtrom di vaser

00:15:26.247 --> 00:15:28.294
un fun a RUCHEY geyt a, vert

00:15:28.294 --> 00:15:29.531
a g- taykh

00:15:30.769 --> 00:15:36.056
 yo, dos iz a MAAYAN, MAAYAN. NACHAL, NACHAL.

00:15:30.870 --> 00:15:32.619
oyf IVRIT NACHAL?

00:15:32.777 --> 00:15:36.039
NACHAL. MAAYA- MAAYAN?

00:15:36.056 --> 00:15:37.209
O MAAYAN.

00:15:37.603 --> 00:15:38.744
ikh ze

00:15:39.477 --> 00:15:41.192
es shteyt a froy

00:15:42.312 --> 00:15:44.207
mit a tikhl oyfn kop

00:15:44.207 --> 00:15:45.529
ayngeboygn

00:15:45.771 --> 00:15:47.300
un shvenkt di vesh.

00:15:48.808 --> 00:15:50.607
ikh bin tsugegangen tsu ir

00:15:52.707 --> 00:15:56.515
un av- azoy vi ikh ken poylish, un ikh veys az zi iz a poylishe

00:15:56.638 --> 00:15:59.647
bin ikh glaykh tsugegangen un gezogt "DZIEN DOBRY PANI.

00:15:59.647 --> 00:16:00.851
gut morgn."

00:16:01.650 --> 00:16:03.416
vi zi hot mir derzen

00:16:03.473 --> 00:16:05.374
un zi hot mir derkent

00:16:06.207 --> 00:16:08.698
az ikh bin a mol geven a lererin

00:16:09.295 --> 00:16:12.967
un zaynen mir ale geven oyf a, oyf a simkhe

00:16:13.075 --> 00:16:14.149
bay ir

00:16:15.201 --> 00:16:18.654
bay zayn, bay dem man's a bruder's a yingl iz geven

00:16:21.121 --> 00:16:22.316
vi zogt men?

00:16:22.423 --> 00:16:27.209
geborn gevorn a kind, iz bay di kristn makhn dokh oykh azoy vi a BRIT MILA.

00:16:28.735 --> 00:16:30.505
bin ikh geven dan ayngeladn

00:16:30.505 --> 00:16:32.765
iz zi zi geven, un zi hot mir dan gezen

00:16:32.802 --> 00:16:35.202
hot zi zikh dermont ver ikh bin

00:16:35.202 --> 00:16:36.752
az ikh bin geven a lererin

00:16:36.752 --> 00:16:38.482
un az ikh bin take a yidishe

00:16:38.910 --> 00:16:40.147
iz fun shrek

00:16:40.147 --> 00:16:41.790
az zi hot mir derzen

00:16:42.083 --> 00:16:43.506
iz bay ir aroysgefaln

00:16:43.506 --> 00:16:45.317
di vesh vos gehaltn in hant

00:16:45.525 --> 00:16:46.582
aropgefaln.

00:16:46.825 --> 00:16:49.789
un zi iz gevorn vays, vays fun shrek.

00:16:52.039 --> 00:16:53.113
zog ikh

00:16:53.187 --> 00:16:55.645
"CZY MOGE POBYT U PANSTWA?

00:16:55.920 --> 00:16:58.158
tsi ikh ken bay aykh zayn?"

00:16:59.329 --> 00:17:01.483
hot zi farbrokhn beyde hent.

00:17:02.029 --> 00:17:03.949
zogt zi "CO PANI MOWI?

00:17:03.949 --> 00:17:06.759
KOCHAC BLIZNIEGO JAK SIEBIE SAMEGO."

00:17:06.759 --> 00:17:08.434
oyf yidish heyst dos

00:17:09.150 --> 00:17:12.299
me darf lib hobn dem khaver vi zikh aleyn.

00:17:13.723 --> 00:17:17.244
mit di verter, di gleybike verter

00:17:19.258 --> 00:17:21.851
zi hot alts ibergelozn bay di vaser.

00:17:22.228 --> 00:17:24.955
zi hot mir genumen untern orem.

00:17:25.182 --> 00:17:27.302
zi hot aropgenumen fun zikh

00:17:27.425 --> 00:17:29.279
dem shal vos zi hot gehat

00:17:29.279 --> 00:17:31.989
fun vol. zi hot mir tsugedekt

00:17:31.989 --> 00:17:33.669
kloymersht az ikh bin

00:17:33.889 --> 00:17:35.267
a shkheyne ire

00:17:35.610 --> 00:17:37.392
un arayngefirt mir

00:17:37.669 --> 00:17:39.013
in a shtal.

00:17:40.487 --> 00:17:42.303
in a shtal iz geven

00:17:42.462 --> 00:17:44.886
a mol iz dos geven a hoyz.

00:17:45.482 --> 00:17:48.676
nor ven der balebos hot oysgeboyt

00:17:48.676 --> 00:17:49.956
a naye hoyz

00:17:49.956 --> 00:17:51.566
iz di alte geblibn.

00:17:51.861 --> 00:17:53.666
iz der oyvn geshtanen

00:17:53.666 --> 00:17:55.816
un di vent ayngefaln ⟨vos⟩ zaynen geshtanen

00:17:55.830 --> 00:17:57.744
a fentster iz geven aza.

00:17:58.105 --> 00:17:59.983
der dakh iz geven fun shtroy.

00:17:59.983 --> 00:18:01.544
ober dortn zaynen geven

00:18:01.544 --> 00:18:04.250
ferd un beheymes un tsign

00:18:04.250 --> 00:18:05.890
un endikes un hiner

00:18:05.890 --> 00:18:07.750
ober dos iz geven alts tse-

00:18:07.750 --> 00:18:09.826
ibergetsoymt, tseteylt, tseteylt.

00:18:10.069 --> 00:18:11.379
un s'iz geven

00:18:11.487 --> 00:18:13.118
a rusisher oyvn.

00:18:14.237 --> 00:18:17.623
zogt zi "FANYA DAVIDOVNA, ot do vet zayn dayn shtub

00:18:18.135 --> 00:18:19.766
un do vestu lebn."

00:18:20.262 --> 00:18:22.435
kh'hob oyfgehoybn di hent tsu got

00:18:22.435 --> 00:18:25.166
ikh trakht take hot got oyf mir rakhmones gehat

00:18:25.273 --> 00:18:28.912
UNK er firt mir tsu gleybike, gute goyim.

00:18:29.644 --> 00:18:31.292
zi iz avek in shtub

00:18:32.293 --> 00:18:34.824
zi hot gebrakht epes alte begodim

00:18:34.824 --> 00:18:37.074
oysgeshpreyt mir oyfn oyvn

00:18:37.074 --> 00:18:38.514
oyf royer shtroy

00:18:38.959 --> 00:18:40.128
oyf di shtroy

00:18:40.128 --> 00:18:41.737
ire alte begodim

00:18:42.503 --> 00:18:46.209
gebrakht epes mir tsukopn epes vos a beged

00:18:46.452 --> 00:18:48.432
ober alts mitn gedank

00:18:48.432 --> 00:18:50.372
zol nit blaybn keyn khshad

00:18:50.372 --> 00:18:52.272
vayl tomer gefint men mir

00:18:53.016 --> 00:18:55.406
vet men dokh glaykh zey bashuldikn.

00:18:55.513 --> 00:18:58.510
iz bay zey shoyn der MOACH hot azoy gearbet

00:18:58.618 --> 00:18:59.489
az zey hobn

00:18:59.496 --> 00:19:02.117
moyre gehat oykh, iz alts geven batrakht.

00:19:02.117 --> 00:19:04.237
hobn zey mir keyn kishn nit gebrakht

00:19:04.237 --> 00:19:06.587
epes oykh alte shmates

00:19:06.668 --> 00:19:08.720
ober far mir iz geven dos zeyer gut.

00:19:08.743 --> 00:19:10.217
un zi hot gezogt "FANYA

00:19:10.217 --> 00:19:12.857
do vestu zayn. du zolst nit aroysgeyn

00:19:14.008 --> 00:19:15.791
keyner zol dir nit zen

00:19:16.523 --> 00:19:17.192
un

00:19:17.653 --> 00:19:18.474
shoyn.

00:19:18.565 --> 00:19:22.322
mir veln dir morgn brengen esn, un azoy vestu do lebn."

00:19:23.188 --> 00:19:24.346
in der

00:19:24.910 --> 00:19:26.963
CHATKA bin ikh geven

00:19:27.441 --> 00:19:29.375
ikh gleyb aza monat tsayt

00:19:29.618 --> 00:19:32.717
vinter. ⟨oyf⟩ gantsn yanuar bin ikh dort geven.

00:19:32.908 --> 00:19:34.083
ikh gleyb azoy.

00:19:35.153 --> 00:19:36.128
in shtub

00:19:36.128 --> 00:19:41.643
iz geven an oremkeyt. zi iz geven a shnayderke. bikhlal iz dortn di bafelkerung iz geven zeyer an oreme.

00:19:44.839 --> 00:19:47.972
hot zi gezogt "in shtub kenstu bay undz nit zayn."

00:19:48.467 --> 00:19:49.220
nor

00:19:49.277 --> 00:19:50.975
⟨zi iz gekumen⟩ zuntik

00:19:51.150 --> 00:19:52.426
oyf iberakhtog

00:19:53.310 --> 00:19:54.468
bay nakht

00:19:54.627 --> 00:19:56.291
shabes tsu nakht

00:19:56.702 --> 00:19:58.603
arayngefirt mir in shtub

00:19:58.710 --> 00:20:00.740
zi hot mir ibergetseylemt

00:20:00.740 --> 00:20:02.670
oyf mir hot zi gemakht dem tseylem.

00:20:03.672 --> 00:20:04.318
un

00:20:04.318 --> 00:20:06.297
gezogt "dos iz mayn mishpokhe.

00:20:06.625 --> 00:20:09.150
mayn man heyst BOLESLAW.

00:20:09.291 --> 00:20:11.512
mayn tokhter heyst ⟨MARECHNA⟩.

00:20:11.721 --> 00:20:13.858
mayn zun heyst ⟨DWADCEK⟩

00:20:15.990 --> 00:20:17.666
un nokh un nokh, fargesn.

00:20:17.666 --> 00:20:18.954
tsvey zin

00:20:19.737 --> 00:20:21.064
un a tokhter.

00:20:25.525 --> 00:20:26.649
"eyn zun

00:20:27.482 --> 00:20:30.120
bay undz iz nito" zogt zi. eyn zun

00:20:30.120 --> 00:20:32.353
hobn di daytshn tsugenumen im

00:20:33.355 --> 00:20:36.167
heyst es, di daytshn hobn verbirt

00:20:36.898 --> 00:20:39.254
dem yugnt fun di poyerim.

00:20:39.953 --> 00:20:45.718
zey voltn dos verbirn, gebn zey gever, un zey voltn geyn shlogn di yidn, rabirn di yidn.

00:20:49.977 --> 00:20:51.439
zogt zi "undzer

00:20:51.580 --> 00:20:54.898
⟨WACEKE⟩ iz nito." ⟨WACEKE⟩ take hot er geheysn.

00:20:54.972 --> 00:20:56.552
"⟨WACEKE⟩ iz nito."

00:20:57.823 --> 00:20:58.846
gevoynt

00:20:58.853 --> 00:21:02.171
dos iz geven azoy sheyn in shtub, azoy eydl fayn

00:21:02.903 --> 00:21:04.663
s'volt kumen zuntik

00:21:04.663 --> 00:21:06.609
voltn zey mir nemen in shtub.

00:21:07.999 --> 00:21:09.545
in di fri zuntik.

00:21:10.480 --> 00:21:15.047
di fentster zol zayn farhangen, oyb s'iz geven bay nakht, di fayer zol zikh nit zen.

00:21:16.318 --> 00:21:18.269
un mir voltn zikh ale

00:21:18.377 --> 00:21:19.755
ale davenen

00:21:20.014 --> 00:21:24.125
azoy vi ikh ken poylish, volt zi mir gebn aza siderl

00:21:24.570 --> 00:21:27.942
un ikh zol oykh mit zey leyenen zeyere tfiles.

00:21:27.942 --> 00:21:29.981
ikh hob zikh tsugepast tsu zey

00:21:30.055 --> 00:21:32.955
zey voltn shteyn oyf di kni un tseylemen zikh.

00:21:32.955 --> 00:21:35.245
mir hot zi nit geheysn shteyn oyf di kni

00:21:35.245 --> 00:21:37.375
un tseylemen zikh gegn Yezusn.

00:21:37.375 --> 00:21:39.565
dos nit, ikh zol shteyn fun vaytn.

00:21:40.365 --> 00:21:41.948
hot mir nit getsvungen

00:21:41.948 --> 00:21:43.532
az ikh zol zikh tseylemen.

00:21:44.567 --> 00:21:45.388
un

00:21:45.478 --> 00:21:48.290
nakher voltn zey zikh tsvishn zikh azoy kushn

00:21:48.567 --> 00:21:50.282
un avekfirn mir

00:21:50.406 --> 00:21:53.963
vayter gebn mir epes onton zeyere zakhn

00:21:53.963 --> 00:21:56.256
un vayter avekfirn oyf mayn oyvn.

00:21:57.240 --> 00:21:58.769
ot azoy hob ikh gelebt

00:21:58.810 --> 00:22:00.255
a monat tsayt.

00:22:01.054 --> 00:22:03.744
nor ikh ken nit fargesn, dortn ⟨lig f-⟩

00:22:03.744 --> 00:22:05.164
oyfn oyvn

00:22:05.164 --> 00:22:07.374
bin ikh geven zikher, mit vos?

00:22:07.374 --> 00:22:09.964
vayl kh'hob gevust az zey hitn mir.

00:22:10.774 --> 00:22:13.240
zey zorgn vegn mayn eksistents.

00:22:13.240 --> 00:22:15.200
az mir vet UNK keyner nit gefinen.

00:22:15.200 --> 00:22:16.601
efsher tsufelik

00:22:16.601 --> 00:22:18.851
ober keyner vet UNK mir nit masern.

00:22:20.072 --> 00:22:22.968
iz do zayendik tsvishn di khayes

00:22:23.481 --> 00:22:26.327
hob ikh shoyn zikh oysgelernt dem untersheyd

00:22:26.603 --> 00:22:28.959
di tsign zogn me, me

00:22:29.792 --> 00:22:30.596
ye?

00:22:30.957 --> 00:22:35.220
un di shepsn zogn oykh me, me, ober dos iz an untersheyd.

00:22:35.395 --> 00:22:37.110
a tsig zogt andersh

00:22:37.369 --> 00:22:39.087
un a sheps zogt andersh

00:22:39.087 --> 00:22:40.265
di gendz

00:22:41.048 --> 00:22:42.257
shrayen

00:22:43.343 --> 00:22:44.893
un entlen

00:22:44.893 --> 00:22:47.313
iz bay undz iz do i gendz i entlen, shrayen

00:22:47.313 --> 00:22:49.793
andersh. gr, gra, gra, gra, gra

00:22:49.793 --> 00:22:50.880
oykh andersh.

00:22:50.920 --> 00:22:52.363
hob ikh shoyn gevust

00:22:52.363 --> 00:22:53.953
dos reydn di khayes

